#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.98" id="98"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: ajjhattikavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "an1.98-139:0.2"
msgid "10. Dutiyapamādādivagga"
msgstr "10. Negligence (2nd)"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:0.3"
msgid "98"
msgstr "98"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc98.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:98.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, pamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very harmful as negligence."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:98.1.2"
msgid "Pamādo, bhikkhave, mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Negligence is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:98.1.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.99" id="99"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:98.1.4"
msgid "99"
msgstr "99"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc99.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:99.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, appamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very beneficial as diligence."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:99.1.2"
msgid "Appamādo, bhikkhave, mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Diligence is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:99.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.100" id="100"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:99.1.4"
msgid "100"
msgstr "100"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc100.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:100.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, kosajjaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very harmful as laziness."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:100.1.2"
msgid "Kosajjaṃ, bhikkhave, mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Laziness is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:100.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.101" id="101"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:100.1.4"
msgid "101"
msgstr "101"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc101.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:101.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, vīriyārambho."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very beneficial as arousing energy."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:101.1.2"
msgid "Vīriyārambho, bhikkhave, mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Arousing energy is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:101.1.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.102" id="102"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:101.1.4"
msgid "102–​109"
msgstr "102–109"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc102.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:102.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, mahicchatā … pe … "
"appicchatā … asantuṭṭhitā … santuṭṭhitā … ayonisomanasikāro … "
"yonisomanasikāro … asampajaññaṃ … sampajaññaṃ … dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very harmful as having many wishes … having few wishes … "
"discontent … contentment … improper attention … proper attention … lack of "
"situational awareness … situational awareness …"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.110" id="110"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:102.1.2"
msgid "110"
msgstr "110"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc110.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:110.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Bāhiraṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ "
"mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, pāpamittatā."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account exterior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very harmful as bad friends."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:110.1.2"
msgid "Pāpamittatā, bhikkhave, mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Bad friends are very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:110.1.3"
msgid "Terasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.111" id="111"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:110.1.4"
msgid "111"
msgstr "111"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc111.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:111.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Bāhiraṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ "
"mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, kalyāṇamittatā."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account exterior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very beneficial as good friends."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:111.1.2"
msgid "Kalyāṇamittatā, bhikkhave, mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Good friends are very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:111.1.3"
msgid "Cuddasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.112" id="112"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:111.1.4"
msgid "112"
msgstr "112"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc112.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:112.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, anuyogo akusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very harmful as pursuing bad habits and not good habits."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:112.1.2"
msgid ""
"Anuyogo, bhikkhave, akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Pursuing bad habits and not good habits is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:112.1.3"
msgid "Pannarasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.113" id="113"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:112.1.4"
msgid "113"
msgstr "113"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc113.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:113.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ajjhattikaṃ, bhikkhave, aṅganti karitvā nāññaṃ ekaṅgampi samanupassāmi yaṃ "
"evaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, anuyogo kusalānaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Taking into account interior factors, mendicants, I do not see a single one "
"that is so very beneficial as pursuing good habits and not bad habits."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:113.1.2"
msgid ""
"Anuyogo, bhikkhave, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Pursuing good habits and not bad habits is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:113.1.3"
msgid "Soḷasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.114" id="114"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:113.1.4"
msgid "114"
msgstr "114"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc114.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:114.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, pamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the decline and "
"disappearance of the true teaching like negligence."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:114.1.2"
msgid "Pamādo, bhikkhave, saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Negligence leads to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:114.1.3"
msgid "Sattarasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.115" id="115"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:114.1.4"
msgid "115"
msgstr "115"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc115.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:115.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, "
"appamādo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the continuation, "
"persistence, and enduring of the true teaching like diligence."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:115.1.2"
msgid ""
"Appamādo, bhikkhave, saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya "
"saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Diligence leads to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the true "
"teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:115.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhārasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.116" id="116"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:115.1.4"
msgid "116"
msgstr "116"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc116.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:116.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, kosajjaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the decline and "
"disappearance of the true teaching like laziness."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:116.1.2"
msgid ""
"Kosajjaṃ, bhikkhave, saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "Laziness leads to the decline and disappearance of the true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:116.1.3"
msgid "Ekūnavīsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.117" id="117"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:116.1.4"
msgid "117"
msgstr "117"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc117.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:117.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, "
"vīriyārambho."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the continuation, "
"persistence, and enduring of the true teaching like arousing energy."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:117.1.2"
msgid ""
"Vīriyārambho, bhikkhave, saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya "
"saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Arousing energy leads to the continuation, persistence, and enduring of the "
"true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:117.1.3"
msgid "Vīsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.118" id="118"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:117.1.4"
msgid "118–​128"
msgstr "118–​128"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc118.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:118.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, mahicchatā … pe … "
"appicchatā … asantuṭṭhitā … santuṭṭhitā … ayonisomanasikāro … "
"yonisomanasikāro … asampajaññaṃ … sampajaññaṃ … pāpamittatā … kalyāṇamittatā "
"… anuyogo akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the decline and "
"disappearance of the true teaching like having many wishes … having few "
"wishes … discontent … contentment … improper attention … proper attention … "
"lack of situational awareness … situational awareness … bad friends … good "
"friends … pursuing bad habits, not good habits."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:118.1.2"
msgid ""
"Anuyogo, bhikkhave, akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"saddhammassa sammosāya antaradhānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Pursuing bad habits and not good habits leads to the decline and "
"disappearance of the true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:118.1.3"
msgid "Ekattiṃsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.129" id="129"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:118.1.4"
msgid "129"
msgstr "129"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc129.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:129.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yo evaṃ saddhammassa "
"ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, anuyogo "
"kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that leads to the continuation, "
"persistence, and enduring of the true teaching like pursuing good habits and "
"not bad habits."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:129.1.2"
msgid ""
"Anuyogo, bhikkhave, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ, ananuyogo akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"saddhammassa ṭhitiyā asammosāya anantaradhānāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Pursuing good habits and not bad habits leads to the continuation, "
"persistence, and enduring of the true teaching”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:129.1.3"
msgid "Bāttiṃsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:129.1.4"
msgid "Catukkoṭikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.130" id="130"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:129.1.5"
msgid "130"
msgstr "130"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc130.1"></a>
#. VAR: bahujanaahitāya → bahujanāhitāya (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: bahujanaasukhāya → bahujanāsukhāya (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an1.98-139:130.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū adhammaṃ dhammoti dīpenti te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū "
"bahujanaahitāya paṭipannā bahujanaasukhāya, bahuno janassa anatthāya ahitāya "
"dukkhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, those mendicants who explain what is not the teaching as the "
"teaching are acting for the hurt and unhappiness of the people, for the "
"harm, hurt, and suffering of gods and humans."

#. VAR: cimaṃ → tepimaṃ (si)
msgctxt "an1.98-139:130.1.2"
msgid ""
"Bahuñca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū apuññaṃ pasavanti, te cimaṃ saddhammaṃ "
"antaradhāpentī”ti."
msgstr "They make much bad karma and make the true teaching disappear.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:130.1.3"
msgid "Tettiṃsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.131" id="131"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:130.1.4"
msgid "131"
msgstr "131"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc131.1"></a>
#. VAR: te → yepi te (s1-3)
msgctxt "an1.98-139:131.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū dhammaṃ adhammoti dīpenti te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū "
"bahujanaahitāya paṭipannā bahujanaasukhāya, bahuno janassa anatthāya ahitāya "
"dukkhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, those mendicants who explain what is the teaching as not the "
"teaching are acting for the hurt and unhappiness of the people, for the "
"harm, hurt, and suffering of gods and humans."

msgctxt "an1.98-139:131.1.2"
msgid ""
"Bahuñca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū apuññaṃ pasavanti, te cimaṃ saddhammaṃ "
"antaradhāpentī”ti."
msgstr "They make much bad karma and make the true teaching disappear.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.98-139:131.1.3"
msgid "Catuttiṃsatimaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.132" id="132"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:131.1.4"
msgid "132–​139"
msgstr "132–139"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc132.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.98-139:132.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū avinayaṃ vinayoti dīpenti … pe … vinayaṃ "
"avinayoti dīpenti … pe … abhāsitaṃ alapitaṃ tathāgatena bhāsitaṃ lapitaṃ "
"tathāgatenāti dīpenti … pe … bhāsitaṃ lapitaṃ tathāgatena abhāsitaṃ alapitaṃ "
"tathāgatenāti dīpenti … pe … anāciṇṇaṃ tathāgatena āciṇṇaṃ tathāgatenāti "
"dīpenti … pe … āciṇṇaṃ tathāgatena anāciṇṇaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti … pe … "
"apaññattaṃ tathāgatena paññattaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti … pe … paññattaṃ "
"tathāgatena apaññattaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti;"
msgstr ""
"“Those mendicants who explain non-Vinaya as Vinaya … Vinaya as non-Vinaya … "
"what was not spoken and stated by the Realized One as spoken and stated by "
"the Realized One … what was spoken and stated by the Realized One as not "
"spoken and stated by the Realized One … what was not practiced by the "
"Realized One as practiced by the Realized One … what was practiced by the "
"Realized One as not practiced by the Realized One … what was not prescribed "
"by the Realized One as prescribed by the Realized One … what was prescribed "
"by the Realized One as not prescribed by the Realized One …"

msgctxt "an1.98-139:132.1.2"
msgid ""
"te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū bahujanaahitāya paṭipannā bahujanaasukhāya, bahuno "
"janassa anatthāya ahitāya dukkhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""
